    <published>2015-01-13T08:05:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-01-13T10:13:27.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <strong>Markdown</strong> 是一种轻量级标记语言，创始人为約翰·格魯伯（John Gruber）。它允许人们使用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML(或者HTML)文档.这种语言吸收了很多在电子邮件中已有的纯文本标记的特性.<br> 本文介绍Markdown常用语法,内容虽少,但都是最常用的基本语法,并且用hexo编写post时都可以直接使用.</p>
<h3 id="换行">换行</h3>
<p>可以在行尾输入两个或以上的空格，然后回车。 这样插入换行十分麻烦，但是,若每个换行都转换为'/<br>',在 Markdown中显然并不合适，所以只有在你确定你需要时,手动添加。在hexo中直接输入/也是可以的.</p>
<h3 id="强调">强调</h3>
<p>注: <strong><em>'*'与'_'效果相同.</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>*content*与_content_表示斜体</li>
<li>**content**与__content__表示粗体</li>
<li>***content***与___content___表示斜体并加粗<br><br><br><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">*</span>The devil is in the details.<span class="keyword">*</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span>The devil is in the details.<span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span>The devil is in the details.<span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><em>The devil is in the details.</em><br><strong>The devil is in the details.</strong><br><strong><em>The devil is in the details.</em></strong><br><br><br><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">_The devil <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> the details._</div><div class="line">__The devil <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> the details.__</div><div class="line">___The devil <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> the details.___</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><em>The devil is in the details.</em><br><strong>The devil is in the details.</strong><br><strong><em>The devil is in the details.</em></strong></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
